URL: https://www.chef.io/

Chef is an automation tool that provides a way to define infrastructure as code. Infrastructure as code (IAC) 
simply means that managing infrastructure by writing code (Automating infrastructure) rather than using manual processes.
Chef uses a pure-Ruby, domain-specific language (DSL) for writing system configurations.

Chef has a Client-Server architecture. But Chef has an extra component called Workstation



